# bundles/ -- drop-in directory for MSIs the installer should bundle.
# Currently only LogMeIn.msi is recognized; future per-vendor bundles
# will land here too (Carbonite installer, Veeam Agent, etc.) once we
# settle the licensing question for redistributing those.
#
# This folder is COMMITTED so CI can pick up the MSI on every build,
# but we ignore everything else by default so half-renamed downloads
# or wrong files don't end up in the repo.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LogMeIn.msi
